title: Live At The Casino - The Late Show! DCYoungFly, Karlous Miller & Chico Bean | Ep. 241
itunes:title: Live At The Casino - The Late Show! DCYoungFly, Karlous Miller & Chico Bean | Ep. 241
description:
Dc Young Fly, Karlous Miller and Chico Bean deliver a legendary performance in the second of two sold out shows in Mashantucket, Connecticut at the Foxwoods Resort and Casino. This a roast session like no other - this crowd is def one of the livest and diverse and the fellas waste no time showing the people love, bringing the laughs and keeping it all the way REAL! This one for the #85percenters!
